OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBT customers unknowingly   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcharged for Xbox Game Pass 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some BT customers are being signed up  
OL,6, to, and charged for, Xbox Game Pass    
OL,7, without their knowledge or consent.    
OL,9,FAn extra #10 per month was added to    
OL,10,Ftheir internet bill, despite them not  
OL,11,Frequesting the gaming subscription.    
OL,13,FCustomers have been complaining about  
OL,14,Fthe issue on BT's online forums for    
OL,15,Fseveral months. Those the BBC spoke to 
OL,16,Fhad their money refunded but described 
OL,17,Ftheir experiences as worrying.         
OL,19,FBT apologised and advised customers to 
OL,20,Fbe on the lookout for similar problems.
